<div class="ribbon ribbon__sub"><h2 class="ribbon--heading"><span>G</span>et in touch</h2></div> {{#sent}}<p>Your message has been sent to Maria, thanks. She'll contact you as soon as possible. <a href="/">Return to homepage</a></p>
{{/sent}} {{^sent}}<p>Contact Maria to book your session today. Phone: <a href="tel:+447796547113">07796 547113</a>, email: <a href="mailto:hello@massagesante.co.uk">hello@massagesante.co.uk</a> or simply use the form below.</p> {{#error}}<div class="error-summary"><p>{{error}}</p> {{#errors}}<ul> {{#errors.all}}<li><a href="#contact-{{id}}">{{message}}</a></li> {{/errors.all}}</ul> {{/errors}}</div> {{/error}}<form action="/contact#content" method="POST"> <label class="name{{#errors.byId.name}} error{{/errors.byId.name}}">Your name: <input type="text" name="contact[name]" value="{{message.name}}" class="error" id="contact-name" /></label> <label class="phone{{#errors.byId.phone}} error{{/errors.byId.phone}}">Your contact number: <input type="tel" name="contact[phone]" value="{{message.phone}}" class="error" id="contact-phone" /></label> and/or <label class="email{{#errors.byId.email}} error{{/errors.byId.email}}">email: <input type="email" name="contact[email]" value="{{message.email}}" class="error" id="contact-email" /></label> <label for="contact-message" class="message{{#errors.byId.message}} error{{/errors.byId.message}}">Your message:</label> <textarea name="contact[message]" id="contact-message" cols="60" rows="10" class="error">{{message.message}}</textarea> <input type="submit" value="Send" class="button" /> <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{token}}" /></form>
